---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets'
import heroImage from '@/assets/images/hero-l.jpg'

---
<section class="relative w-full h-[80vh] overflow-hidden lg:max-h-[75vh]">
  <div class="w-full h-full absolute inset-0 z-10 bg-gradient-to-b from-gradient to-gradient via-transparent" />
  <div class="absolute top-0 z-10 p-10 w-full h-full flex flex-col max-w-lg sm:p-20 justify-center ">
    <h1 class="text-ligth-0 font-normal text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-Grotesk max-w-sm text-balance mb-2 text-accent">Outsourcing & BPO</h1>
    <p class="text-ligth-0 font-bold text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-Grotesk border-b-2 leading-6 py-2 border-accent">¡Asesoría Contable y Financiera que impulsa tu Negocio!</p>
    <p class="text-ligth-0 font-light text-xl lg:text-2xl font-Grotesk leading-5 lg:leading-tight py-2">Deja en manos de expertos la gestión de tus procesos financieros, contables y fiscales, así puedes dedicarte plenamente a impulsar tu negocio.</p>
  </div>
  <picture class="block brightness-50 w-full h-full" >
    <Image
      src={heroImage}
      alt="Hero Image"
      class="w-full h-full object-cover"
    />
  </picture>
</section>
